data.description: Dorchester II schools. Less than 5 miles from Historical Summerville & many fantastic restaurants & shopping. Smooth ceilings. Downstairs offers a formal dining room, eat in kitchen overlooking the backyard AND a separate office/play room/flex space. 42'' staggered cabinets in kitchen. EXTRA wide breakfast bar separates family room from the kitchen- perfect for entertaining. Quartz countertops with custom backsplash. Smooth top range and built in microwave make dinner a breeze! Pendant lighting located over prep island. Built in coffee/bar area AND pantry allow for additional space to store all your culinary items. All NEW carpet upstairs. Laundry room is located at the top of the stairs for convenience & offers lots of natural light. HUGE master bedroom easily accomadates a king size bed& oversized furniture. Master bathroom has dual sink vanity with lots of storage. New tub & shower insert are squeaky clean! Pergo waterproof flooring in both upstairs bathrooms & laundry room. Master bedroom closet is OVERSIZED & offers shelving for shoes/sweaters. Guest bedrooms are nice sized & located on the opposite side of the home, away from the master bedroom for privacy. Backyard has privacy fence with large gate. Huge patio with stone pavers & built in stone bench, perfect for grilling and parties.
